         aria-valuemax="100"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;span style="position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); font-weight: bold; white-space: nowrap; pointer-events: none; z-index: 2; color: #fff;"&gt;
        75%
    &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>

